title: Highlights : Reading 0 - 6 Arsenal Women
body_text:
It's time to relive all the goals from Wednesday's victory over Reading, alongside the return of Leah Williamson, in our official match highlights.
We hit six past the Royals to consolidate our spot at the top of Conti Cup Group D and cruise to the quarter-finals of the competition. In an exemplary performance, Caitlin Foord opened the scoring, Stina Blackstenius was our hat-trick hero, and Laia Codina scored her debut goal for the club.
Leah Williamson capped off her return to the pitch after nine long months with a sumptuous assist for Beth Mead, who then volleyed home with ease.
